A RESOLUTION
1 Commending Kristen Timoteo, the Georgia Public Library Service's 2024 Library Employee
2 of the Year; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Kristen Timoteo was named the 2024 Library Employee of the Year by the
4 Georgia Public Library Service in recognition of her dedication and service to the Grantville
5 Public Library; and
6 WHEREAS, despite facing a sudden and life-altering event in November 2022 when she lost
7 her vision due to complications from Lupus, she has remained committed to her role,
8 adapting to new challenges with resilience and determination; and
9 WHEREAS, through extensive training, the use of screen readers, and a deep familiarity with
10 her work, she continues to perform her duties, lead story times for children, and serve her
11 community with unwavering dedication; and
12 WHEREAS, since joining the Grantville Public Library 14 years ago, she has worked
13 tirelessly to address the needs of local residents, promoting the library as a vital community
14 hub and expanding its outreach efforts; and
